===Noun===
'''[[yield]]-[[to]]-[[maturity]]'''

#{{legal}}: A calculation of [[yield]] on a [[bond]] that takes into account the '''capital gain''' on a '''discount bond''' or '''capital loss''' on a '''premium bond'''.<br>In the case of a discount bond, the yield-to-maturity, '''YTM''', is higher than the '''current yield''', or the '''coupon yield'''.<br>The reverse is true for a '''premium bond''' with '''YTM''' lower than both current yield and coupon yield.